---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI学习运用 - rrxr.xyz">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-8">AI学习运用</h1>
  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">学习笔记</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      <li>AI基础</li>
      <li>应用实践（Excel Copilot, 自媒体AI）</li>
      <li>前沿趋势</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">工具与资源</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      <li>本地模型（Ollama, OpenManus）</li>
      <li>API与教程（DeepSeek 等）</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">实战案例</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">这里将展示AI实战案例。</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

